v6 release (#223)

* v6: Expose concurrent job limit

- Analytics.queue_async_stats_job() now returns instance rather than dict
- Analytics.queue_async_stats_job() can now be called directly (with specifying entity parameter)

* Add support for PROMOTED_ACCOUNT stats entity

* Rename CITIES segmentation name to METROS

* remove Scoped Timeline

* as_user_id is now required parameter

* Add additional optimization enum

* remove tailored_audience_type request parameter

* rename lookalike_expansion to audience_expansion

* Media identifier consistency

https://twittercommunity.com/t/ads-api-version-6/129060#heading--media-identifier-consistency

* change API_VERSION

* Revert "remove Scoped Timeline"

This reverts commit 34264d36272e3013b399d895475ce997df4c4c17.

* mark scoped_timeline as deprecated

* update comment

* update example

* Add helper function

- split_list() can be used for splitting entity ids by a given number
